room_title: Escape room "Insane Asylum" by PanIQ Escape Room San Jose in San Jose
room_address: 2270 B Quimby Rd, San Jose, CA 95122
room_description:
The year is 1956. You have been kidnapped by a secret group of scientists and being used as a guinea-pig for their mind control program. Doctors have held you inside a padded room for weeks now.
There was an emergency at the other side of the institution, so the staff is gone for a while. Probably this is your last chance to escape before they completely brainwash you.
